claim: Bastille Day is the largest regular military parade.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The oldest and largest regular military parade in Europe is held on the morning of 14 July , on the Champs-Élysées in Paris in front of the President of the Republic , along with other French officials and foreign guests .

claim: Bastille Day is the largest regular military parade.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Bastille Day Military Parade  (  or 14 July Military Parade , translation of the French name of Défilé militaire du 14 Juillet  )  is a French military parade that has been held on the morning of 14 July each year in Paris since 1880 , almost without exception .
